{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 72,
  "title": "第七十二章（畏畏）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "民之不畏畏 則大畏將至矣"
    },
    {
      "text": "毋閘亓所居 毋猒亓所生 夫唯弗猒 是以不猒"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人 自知而不自見也 自愛而不自貴也 故去彼取此"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "威，害也。人不畏小害則大害至。大害者，謂死亡也。畏之者當愛精神，承天順地也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂心居神，當寬柔，不當急狹也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人所以生者，以有精神。託空虛，喜清靜，飲食不節，忽道念色，邪僻滿腹，為伐本厭神也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫唯獨不厭精神之人，洗心濯垢，恬泊無欲，則精神居之不厭也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "自知己之得失，不自顯見德美於外，藏之於內。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "自愛其身以保精氣，不自貴高榮名於世。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 21,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "去彼自見、自貴，取此自知、自愛。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "清靜無為謂之居，謙後不盈謂之生，離其清淨，行其躁欲，棄其謙後，任其威權，則物擾而民僻，威不能復制民，民不能堪其威，則上下大潰矣，天誅將至。故曰，民不畏威，則大威至。無狎其所居，無厭其所生，言威力不可任也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不自厭也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不自厭，是以天下莫之厭。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不自見其所知，以光耀行威也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "自貴則物狎厭居生。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 21,
          "end": 22
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
